hadiths[26]{hadithnumber,text}:
1434,"Hazrat Yala bin Umayya Raziallahu anhuma bayan kartey hain ke mainey Hazrat umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) sey puchha ke (Quran ki aayat) (فلیس علیکم جناح ان تقصروا من الصلوٰۃ ان خفتم ان یفتنکم الذین کفروا),''tum par koi gunah nahin ke tum namaz qasr kar lo ba-sharte-ke tumhein dar ho ke kafir tumhein nuqsan pahunchaaeyngey (sey malum hota hai ke qasr namaz khof hi ki haalat key sath khas hai).'' ab to log aman ki haalat mein hain (lihaza namaz qasr nahin kerni chahiye). Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : mujhey bhi is baat par tajjub huwa tha jis par tujhey tajjub huwa hai to mainey is barey mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey puchha. aap ney farmaya : ye sadqa hai jo Allah Taala ney tum par kiya hai, to tum Allah Taala ka sadqa qubul karo."
1435,Hazrat Umayya bin Abdullah bin Khalid ney Hazrat Abdullah bin umr Raziallahu anhuma sey kaha : hum Quran Majeed mein ghar ki namaz aur khof ki namaz paatey hain lekin safar ki namaz Quran Majeed mein nahin paatey. Hazrat ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma ney un sey kaha : aey merey bhateejey ! tehqiq Allah Taala ney Hazrat Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko hamari taraf (Nabi bana kar) bheja jab ke hum kuchh nahin jantey they. hum to sirf is tarah kerengey jis tarah hamney Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko kartey dekha hai.
1436,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) Makka sey Madina ki taraf nikley (aur chaar rakat wali namazein) do rakat hi padhtey rahey, halanke Rabbul-Aalameen key siwa aap ko kisi ka dar na tha."
1437,Hazrat ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma bayan kartey hain ke hum Makka Mukarrama aur Madina Munawra key darmiyan Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key sath safar kar rahey they. hamein Allah Taala key siwa kisi ka khof na tha magar hum (rubaai namaz) do rakat padhtey they.
1438,Hazrat ibn Samt bayan kartey hain ke mainey Hazrat umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) ko Zul-Hulefa key maqam par (koi rubaai namaz) do rakat padhtey dekha. mainey un sey is barey mein puchha to unhoney farmaya : main to isi tarah karta hun jis tarah mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko kartey dekha hai.
1439,Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key sath Madina Munawra sey Makka Mukarrama gaya. aap wapis Madina Munawra aaney tak namaz qasr kartey rahey. aap Makkey mein das din thehrey they.
1440,Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) farmatey hain ke mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key sath safar mein (chaar rakat wali namaz) do rakat padhi. Hazrat Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) key sath bhi do rakat padhi aur Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) key sath bhi do rakat padhi.
1441,"Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Jumey ki namaz, eidul-fitr ki namaz, qurbani ( eidul-Azha ) ki namaz aur safar ki namaz Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki zabani do do rakat hai aur ye mukammal hai. is mein koi naqs aur kami nahin."
1442,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma bayan kartey hain ke ghar ki namaz tumharey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki zabani chaar rakat, safar ki namaz do rakat aur khof ki namaz eik rakat farz ki gaee hai."
1443,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma farmatey hain : Allah Taala ney tumharey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki zabani ghar ki namaz chaar rakat, safar mein do rakat aur khof ki haalat main eik rakat farz ki hai."
1444,"Hazrat Musa bin Salma bayan kartey hain ke mainey Hazrat ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma sey puchha ke agar main ba-jamaat namaz na pa sakun to Makka Mukarrama mein namaz kaisey padhun ? unhoney farmaya : do rakatein, ye Abul-Qaasim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki sunnat hai."
1445,"Hazrat Musa bin Salma bayan kartey hain ke mainey Hazrat ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma sey puchha : mujh sey namaz ba-jamaat reh jaey, jab ke main wadi Makka mein hun, to aap key khayal key mutabiq mein kitni rakat namaz padhun? unhoney farmaya : do rakat. ye Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki sunnat hai."
1446,Hazrat Harisa bin Wahab Khuzaai (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke mainey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key sath Mina mein do rakatein padhin halanke aap intehai aman ki haalat mein they aur aap key sathi bhi bahut ziyada they.
1447,Hazrat Harisa bin Wahab Khuzaai (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney hamen mani mein do rakatein padhaain halanke log bahut ziyada they aur intehai aman ki haalat mein they.
1448,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) farmatey hain ke mainey Mina mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key sath, Hazrat abu-Bakar aur Hazrat umr Raziallahu anhuma key sath do rakatein padhin aur Hazrat Usman (Raziallahu anhu) key sath bhi un ki amaarat key ibtidaai zamaney mein do rakatein hi padhin"
1449,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul hai, farmaya : mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key sath Mina mein do rakatein padhin"
1450,Hazrat Abdur-Rehman bin Yazid sey marwi hai ke Hazrat Usman (Raziallahu anhu) ney Mina mein chaar rakatein padhin yahan tak ke ye baat Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ko pahunchi to unhoney farmaya : mainey to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key sath do rakatein hi padhi hain.
1451,Hazrat ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma bayan kartey hain ke mainey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key sath Mina mein do rakatein padhin Hazrat abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) key sath do rakatein padhin aur Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) key sath bhi do rakatein padhin
1452,Hazrat Abdullah bin umr Raziallahu anhuma bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney Mina mein do rakatein padhin Hazrat abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ney bhi yahan do rakatein hi padhin Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ney bhi do hi padhin aur Hazrat Usman (Raziallahu anhu) ney bhi apni khilaafat ki ibtida (shuruat) mein do rakatein hi padhin
1453,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul hai, farmatey hain, hum Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key sath Madina Munawra sey Makka Mukarrama ko nikley. aap wapis Madina tashrif laney tak hamen do rakat hi padhatey rahey. (shagrid Abu Is-haq bayan kartey hain ke ) mainey kaha : kya aap Makka mein thehrey they? unhoney farmaya : han, hum Makka mein das din thehrey they."
1454,Hazrat ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) Makka Mukarrama mein pandarah din thehrey. do-do rakat padhtey rahey.
1455,"Hazrat Ala bin Hizrami (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : muhaajir shakhs apna Haj o Umra pura karney key baad sirf teen din makkey mein reh sakta hai."
1456,"Hazrat Ala bin Hizrami (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : ( makkey sey) hijrat karney wala apna Haj o Umra pura karney key baad teen din ( makkey mein) thahar sakta hai."
1457,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai ke main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key sath Madina Munawra sey Makka Mukarrama Umra karney gaee yahan tak ke jab main Makka aai to mainey kaha : aey Allah key Rasool! merey maa baap aap par fida hon! aap namaze-Qasr kartey rahey, main puri padhti rahi. aap roza chhodtey rahey, main rakhti rahi. aap ney farmaya : Aaisha! tuney theek kya. aap ney mujh par us baat ka aeb nahin lagaya."
1458,"Hazrat Wabra bin Abdur-Rehman bayan kartey hain ke Hazrat ibne-Umar safar mein do rakaaton sey zayed nahin padhtey they, na ( un do rakaaton sey) pehley kuch padhtey na baad mein. un sey kaha gaya : ye kya tariqa hai? to unhoney kaha : mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko aisey hi kartey dekha hai."
1459,"Hazrat Hafs bin Aasim bayan kartey hain ke main Hazrat ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma key sath eik safar mein tha unhoney Zohar aur Asr do-do rakat padhin phir apni bichhi hui chataai ki taraf gaey. unhoney kuch logon ko dekha ke wo nafl (sunnatein) padh rahey hain. unhoney puchha : ye log kya padh rahey hain? mainey arz kya : nafl padh rahey hain. unhoney farmaya : agar main farzon sey pehley ya baad mein sunnatein padhtey to main farz hi mukammal padh leta. main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key sath raha hun, aap to safar mein do rakaaton sey zayed na padhtey they. isi tarah Hazrat abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) key sath raha. yahan tak ke wo faut ho gaey. isi tarah Hazrat umr aur Hazrat Usman Raziallahu anhuma key sath."
